snippet.title: Amber Heard: 10 Facts, Movies & Red Carpet
snippet.description:
Subscribe to my channel: https://www.youtube.com/bykrystyna
My website: http://urbanandstylish.com
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/bykrystyna
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/bykrystyna
Business Inquiries: krystyna@urbanandstylish.com

Here are some cool facts about Amber Heard.

Amber Heard was born in Austin, Texas. 

Dropped out of school at 17 and moved to NY to model but later on relocated to LA for acting

Amber is best known for Zombieland, Danish Girl, Drive Angry and now playing Mera in Justice League 

Amber Heard  first acting gig was in a TV show - Hidden Palms

Amber Heard first big screen role was in “Friday nights lights” in 2004

She likes to read and says “knowledge is my religion” and can talk about literature for hours. 

She came out as bisexual at the 25th Anniversary Celebration of GLAAD

Heard is a certified lifeguard

She speaks Spanish and hand sign language.
